# 001. Use i18Nexus for internationalization

Date: 2022-07-05

## Status

Accepted

## Context

Solution to avoid hardcoded strings in application.

## Decision

Internationalization framework [i18next](https://www.i18next.com/) give us control over string in whole application.
We can change it, translate it (in future) and adding new text. Strings are splited by pages.

## Consequences

Full control over application texts without touching code.

